.html\">Browse</a>\n128:     <a href=\"A-08-favorites.html\">Favorites</a>\n129:     <a href=\"A-09-inquiries.html\">My Inquiries</a>\n130:     <a href=\"A-10-profile.html\">Profile</a>\n131:   </div>\n132: </nav>\n133: \n134: <section class=\"section\">\n135:   <a href=\"A-06-search.html\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:#94A3B8;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px;transition:color 0.2s\" onmouseover=\"this.style.color='#F1F5F9'\" onmouseout=\"this.style.color='#94A3B8'\">\n136:     <span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:arrow-left\" style=\"width:18px\"></span> Back to search\n137:   </a>\n138: \n139:   <div style=\"position:relative;margin-bottom:24px\">\n140:     <div class=\"gallery-img\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.35),rgba(124,58,237,0.35))\"></div>\n141:   </div>\n142: \n143:   <div class=\"thumb-strip\">\n144:     <div class=\"thumb active\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.35),rgba(124,58,237,0.35))\"></div>\n145:     <div class=\"thumb\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.3),rgba(124,58,237,0.5))\"></div>\n146:     <div class=\"thumb\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(124,58,237,0.4),rgba(74,144,217,0.3))\"></div>\n147:     <div class=\"thumb\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.4),rgba(124,58,237,0.2))\"></div>\n148:     <div class=\"thumb\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(124,58,237,0.3),rgba(74,144,217,0.5))\"></div>\n149:   </div>\n150: \n151:   <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin:32px 0 4px\">\n152:     <h2 style=\"font-size:36px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em\">$1,850<small style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:400;color:#94A3B8\">/mo</small></h2>\n153:     <span class=\"badge badge-new\">Available Now</span>\n154:     <button class=\"fav-btn active\" style=\"margin-left:auto\">\n155:       <span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:heart\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>\n156:     </button>\n157:   </div>\n158:   <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#94A3B8;margin-bottom:32px\">\n159:     <span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:map-marker\" style=\"width:16px;vertical-align:-2px\"></span>\n160:     321 Elm St, Austin, TX 78701 &mdash; Downtown Austin\n161:   </p>\n162: \n163:   <div class=\"stats-grid\" style=\"margin-bottom:40px\">\n164:     <div class=\"stat-card\">\n165:       <p><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:bed\" style=\"width:20px;color:#4A90D9;vertical-align:-3px\"></span></p>\n166:       <h3>2</h3>\n167:       <p>Bedrooms</p>\n168:     </div>\n169:     <div class=\"stat-card\">\n170:       <p><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:shower\" style=\"width:20px;color:#4A90D9;vertical-align:-3px\"></span></p>\n171:       <h3>2</h3>\n172:       <p>Bathrooms</p>\n173:     </div>\n174:     <div class=\"stat-card\">\n175:       <p><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:square-foot\" style=\"width:20px;color:#4A90D9;vertical-align:-3px\"></span></p>\n176:       <h3>1,050</h3>\n177:       <p>Square Feet</p>\n178:     </div>\n179:     <div class=\"stat-card\">\n180:       <p><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:office-building\" style=\"width:20px;color:#4A90D9;vertical-align:-3px\"></span></p>\n181:       <h3 style=\"font-size:18px\">Apartment</h3>\n182:       <p>Property Type</p>\n183:     </div>\n184:   </div>\n185: \n186:   <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 420px;gap:40px\">\n187:     <div>\n188:       <div style=\"margin-bottom:40px\">\n189:         <h3 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px\">Description</h3>\n190:         <p style=\"color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8\">\n191:           Welcome to this stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment in the heart of Downtown Austin. This recently renovated unit features floor-to-ceiling windows with panoramic city views, hardwood floors throughout, and a gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. The open-concept living area flows seamlessly onto a private balcony, perfect for entertaining or enjoying Austin's beautiful sunsets. Located just steps from the best restaurants, bars, and entertainment that downtown has to offer. Building amenities include a rooftop pool, state-of-the-art fitness center, and 24/7 concierge service. Includes one assigned parking spot in a secure garage.\n192:         </p>\n193:       </div>\n194: \n195:       <div style=\"margin-bottom:40px\">\n196:         <h3 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px\">Amenities</h3>\n197:         <div class=\"amenities-grid\">\n198:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:wifi\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>High-Speed Internet</div>\n199:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:air-conditioner\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Central Air Conditioning</div>\n200:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:washing-machine\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>In-Unit Laundry</div>\n201:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:dishwasher\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Dishwasher</div>\n202:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:parking\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Assigned Parking</div>\n203:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:dumbbell\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Fitness Center</div>\n204:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:pool\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Rooftop Pool</div>\n205:           <div class=\"amenity-item\"><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:paw\" style=\"width:20px\"></span>Pet Friendly</div>\n206:         </div>\n207:       </div>\n208: \n209:       <div style=\"margin-bottom:40px\">\n210:         <h3 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px\">Location</h3>\n211:         <div class=\"map-placeholder\">\n212:           <span><span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:map\" style=\"width:20px;vertical-align:-4px\"></span> Map &mdash; 321 Elm St, Austin, TX 78701</span>\n213:         </div>\n214:       </div>\n215:     </div>\n216: \n217:     <div>\n218:       <div class=\"card\" style=\"position:sticky;top:24px\">\n219:         <h3 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px\">Send an Inquiry</h3>\n220:         <p style=\"color:#94A3B8;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:20px\">Interested? Send a message to the landlord.</p>\n221:         <form style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px\">\n222:           <div>\n223:             <label for=\"name\">Full Name</label>\n224:             <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"John Smith\">\n225:           </div>\n226:           <div>\n227:             <label for=\"email\">Email Address</label>\n228:             <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"john@example.com\">\n229:           </div>\n230:           <div>\n231:             <label for=\"phone\">Phone Number</label>\n232:             <input type=\"tel\" id=\"phone\" placeholder=\"(512) 555-0142\">\n233:           </div>\n234:           <div>\n235:             <label for=\"message\">Message</label>\n236:             <textarea id=\"message\" placeholder=\"Hi, I'm interested in this property and would like to schedule a viewing...\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n237:           </div>\n238:           <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" style=\"width:100%\">\n239:             <span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:send\" style=\"width:18px\"></span> Send Inquiry\n240:           </button>\n241:         </form>\n242:       </div>\n243:     </div>\n244:   </div>\n245: </section>\n246: </div>\n247: </body>\n248: </html>\n\n(End of file - total 248 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" conten